snippet.title: Abraca – Video game – Fairy tales with an Ankama twist
snippet.description:
Abraca: a strange fairytale kingdom with an Ankama twist in which two to four players take turns playing as princes, princesses and monsters! Discover three different styles of gameplay in the pictures we’ve posted while you wait for this party game to be released on Steam!

Find out more at: http://www.abracagame.com/en
